{"tid":536722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"775億人仔借予1,493空殼企業！浦發銀行被罰","createTime":"2018-01-22T05:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T08:32:28.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b4bee2dc815861794037775bb4d27e7093097219","tid":536722,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T05:37:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180122/large/1516593658_93dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180122%2Flarge%2F1516593658_93dd.jpg&h=362bb712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川銀監局近日依法查處浦發銀行成都分行違規發放貸款案件，罰款4.62億元人民幣，對浦發銀行成都分行原行長、兩名副行長、一名部門負責人和一名支行行長分別給予禁止終身從事銀行業工作、取消高級管理人員任職資格、警告及罰款。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，銀監會在現場檢查中發現，浦發銀行成都分行爲掩蓋不良貸款，通過編造虛假用途、分拆授信、越權審批等手法，違規辦理信貸、同業、理財、信用證和保理等業務，向1,493個空殼企業授信775億元人民幣，換取相關企業出資承擔浦發銀行成都分行不良貸款。"},{"pid":"a86f01023077e83881f493b8a072fe6d9cd665f0","tid":536722,"uid":12511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T06:03:39.000Z","msg":"借比自己開既公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4966445e86f40b4af7a27395de65029c9ef3225c","tid":536722,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}